{"tid":1628690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國分化撚好鐘意用民意綁架勇武","createTime":"2019-10-06T04:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T05:12:37.000Z","uid":21220,"like":35,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f077eccfa957192d701964e3663cd80ecf0eade6","tid":1628690,"uid":21220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:12:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">熱門啲分化post多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入去睇 唔理係搞黨鐵搞書局搞銀行<br />\n全部都叫唔好過火 會冇哂民意<br />\n民意一早歸邊唔會再搞<br />\n搞紅店黑店完全冇問題 佢地係敵人黎<br />\n勇武識得分邊啲要搞邊啲唔好搞<br />\n唔好再拎民意綁架勇武<br />\n咁樣只會乜都做唔倒<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5a4b96135de78b8e292c196dc399d4ec9d1e17ff","tid":1628690,"uid":21220,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:16:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d725c539c24317472c6855cca7fef0f63fb94a","tid":1628690,"uid":147664,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:18:06.000Z","msg":"2014個招 擺到今日竟然仲work<br />\n當日就講衝就輸 失民意<br />\n今日就講裝修輸國際線<br />\n完全係同一招數"},{"pid":"c86699d38fcc2a4dbe5e994159460466f2fba9ce","tid":1628690,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"佢哋用嚟用去都係呢一招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261d7ae7f7eb12188e15edd11cdffc9d8a3163e7","tid":1628690,"uid":21220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:19:49.000Z","msg":"P牌多撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e0f0e174eab1e444a70fe2e1a6e2216c627655","tid":1628690,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike"